com.fns.grivet.model

Class Class

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fns.grivet.model.Class
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class Class
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A Class is akin to an abstract base Class but is constrained to the definition of member variables. A Class may be linked to a JSON Schema for purposes of validating an object's attributes (expressed in JSON format).
    Author:
    Chris Phillipson
    See Also:
    ClassAttribute, Serialized Form
